<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <meta name="description" content="Personal website for Cristiano Silva Jr.">
        <title>Hello!</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/purecss@0.6.2/build/pure-min.css" integrity="sha384-" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/purecss@0.6.2/build/grids-responsive-min.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/font-awesome/4.0.3/css/font-awesome.css">
        <style>
            {{.Style}}
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>

        <div class="header">
            <div class="home-menu pure-menu pure-menu-horizontal pure-menu-fixed">
                <a class="pure-menu-heading" href=""><i class="fa fa-smile-o"></i>
					Cris Silva Jr.
				</a>

                <ul class="pure-menu-list">
                    <li class="pure-menu-item pure-menu-selected"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Tour</a></li>
                    <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Sign Up</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="splash-container">
            <div class="splash">
                <h1 class="splash-head">Cris Silva Jr.</h1>
                <p class="splash-subhead">
                    Control &amp; Automation Engineer
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content-wrapper">
            <div class="content">
                <h2 class="content-head is-center">What can I offer you?</h2>

                <div class="pure-g">
                    <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-2">

                        <h3 class="content-subhead">
                            <i class="fa fa-bolt"></i>
                            Control &amp; Automation Engineering
                        </h3>
                        <p>
                            I work with Digital Signal Processing.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-2">
                        <h3 class="content-subhead">
                            <i class="fa fa-sitemap"></i>
                            Professional Organizer
                        </h3>
                        <p>
                            I can help you organize your time and your spaces.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="ribbon l-box-lrg pure-g">
                <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
<!--                    <img width="300" alt="File Icons" class="pure-img-responsive" src="img/common/file-icons.png">-->
                </div>
                <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">

                    <h2 class="content-head content-head-ribbon">What have I already built?</h2>

                    <p>
                        Let's talk about my EDF+ lib implementation, Failproof Checklists, Logey and thw whatnot.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <h2 class="content-head is-center">How can you find me?</h2>

                <div class="pure-g">
                    <div class="l-box-lrg pure-u-1 pure-u-md-3-5">
                        <h4>Send me an e-mail!</h4>
                        <p>
                            I think I should add my e-mail here.
                        </p>

                        <h4>More Information...</h4>
                        <p>
                            Add my social media links here...
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

        </div>

        <script type="text/javascript">
            {{.Script}}
        </script>
    </body>
</html>
